'''Tamaḍunt''' (s [[Tutlayt Taɛṛabt|tsrɣint]] : مرض) tga kullu man usnulfu nɣ assnfl illan g [[Tadusi|tdusi]] n ufgan nɣ n kra n [[Amaddar|umaddar]] yaḍni, assnfl ad mqqar iga afggan (izdi d [[Tafgga n ufgan|tfgga]]) nɣ animan (izdi d [[iman]]).

Tamaḍunt tmzaray f waṭṭan (aṭṭan). ig a nsawwal f waṭṭan at ar nsawwal f ufsar (tazzla n ufsar) n kra n tmaḍunt g kra n tmazirt.

== Aṭṭan : ==
Aṭṭan (Asgt : Aṭṭanen nɣ Aṭṭann)

==Timaḍunin tifgganin (tin [[Tafgga n ufgan|tafgga]]) :==

*[[Akucm]] : Assaɣ n tmaḍunt n kra n ufgan ur iɣayn a ismass iḍaṛn ns nɣ ifassn nɣ kra n udɣaṛ yaḍni g tfgga ns.
*[[Abukḍ]] : Tamaḍunt n [[Tiṭṭ|twallin]].
*[[Abiḍṛ]] : Tamaḍunt n [[Aḍaṛ|iḍaṛn]].
*[[Ttufis]]
*[[Tawla]] : Attuy nɣ aqqlay n [[taẓɣlt]] (température).
*[[Buglib]]
*[[Aḍḍuṛḍṛ]] : Tamaḍunt n [[Amẓẓug|imzgan]] (amẓẓug nɣ amẓẓuɣ)
*[[Aẓẓnẓl]] : Tamaḍunt n wanna ur iɣayn a isawl s imi ns (tamaḍunt n [[Awal|wawwal]]).
*[[Buḥmṛun]]
*[[Ẓṛbiyyun]]
*[[Tikḍit]]
*[[Taylalt]]

==Timaḍunin tinimanin (tin [[iman]]) :==
*[[Axlu]] nɣ ammaɛḍṛ : Tamaḍunt n ufgan mi  ilaḥ [[anlli]] (lɛaqql) ns.
*[[Axuftu]] : Tamaḍunt n ufgan ur sul izzgan yat, ur sul a iswingim mzyan ula a ittɛaqqal mzyan (tga tamaḍunt n middn imqqurn g lɛmṛ).
*[[Adduhdu]] : Tmaḍunt n ufgan m ifta [[Anlli|unlli]] (lɛaqql) ns imiqq yaɣɣuld (zund kra n yan iskrn kra n ungas (lksida) ).

